                            <comment id="15610713" author="dongjoon" created="Thu, 27 Oct 2016 05:21:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=zwu.net%40gmail.com&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;zwu.net@gmail.com&quot;&gt;zwu.net@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
Thank you for reporting. BTW, why do you use the following? The default value of `spark.sql.caseSensitive` is `false`, isn&apos;t it?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
